property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT
    "MaterialMovement"."ID"                         AS "ID",
    "MaterialMovement"."CreatedBy_ID"               AS "CreatedBy",
    "MaterialMovement"."MaterialMasterPlant_ID"     AS "MaterialMasterPlant",
    "MaterialMovement"."MovementDirection"          AS "MovementDirection",
    "MaterialMovement"."Amount"                     AS "Amount",
    "MaterialMovement"."Currency"                   AS "Currency",
    "MaterialMovement"."SourceSystemInstance"       AS "SourceSystemInstance",
    "MaterialMovement"."MaterialMovementNumber"     AS "MaterialMovementNumber",
    "MaterialMovement"."StorageLocation"            AS "StorageLocation",
    "MaterialMovement"."MovementQuantityUnit"       AS "MovementQuantityUnit",
    "MaterialMovement"."MovementQuantity"           AS "MovementQuantity",
    "MaterialMovement"."MaterialTransactionType"    AS "MaterialTransactionType",
    "MaterialMovement"."CreationTime"               AS "CreationTime",
    CASE
        WHEN "DeliveryLine"."ID" IS NOT NULL
        THEN "MaterialMovement"."DeliveryLine_ID"
    END                                             AS "DeliveryLine"
FROM "o_custom_MaterialMovement" AS "MaterialMovement"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_DeliveryLine" AS "DeliveryLine"
        ON "MaterialMovement"."DeliveryLine_ID" = "DeliveryLine"."ID"
WHERE "MaterialMovement"."MaterialTransactionType" IN (
    'GoodsIssue',
    'GoodsIssueForStockTransportOrder',
    'GoodsIssueForCrossCompanyStockTransportOrder',
    'GoodsIssueForStockTransportOrderOneStep',
    'GoodsIssueForCrossCompanyStockTransportOrderOneStep',
    'GoodsIssueForSTO',
    'GoodsIssueFromCustomerConsignment',
    'GoodsIssueFromReturnablePackagingStock',
    'GoodsIssueForSalesOrder'
)
